content:
Each primal contains in its data unit a dose of metaprimal energy that aims to help the development and evolution of the human species.

In the first phase are revealed 121 primals PFP, divided in 11 characters, 11 tags and 4 existential states: Primordial, Primitive, Cardinal, Elemental.

The rarest are Primordial and the most common are Elemental. Between them are Primitive and Cardinal, who have special properties that activates Primal Expansion Lab. – designed to give utility to PRIMAL nfts and aimed for sustainable development.
